OL,3,CThe return of The Zutons: Liverpool
OL,4,Cband back on the road
OL,6,FRodgers said: "They reached out to me,
OL,7,Fthey sent me some demos which I liked
OL,8,Fright away and I just can't help it, I
OL,9,Flove good music. And then I realised
OL,10,Fthat these were the guys who did
OL,11,FValerie and I was like, I'm into this."
OL,13,FHe refers to the smash hit Amy
OL,14,FWinehouse track, written and
OL,15,Foriginally performed by The Zutons.
OL,17,FThe band say they had such a good time
OL,18,Frecording the album they didn't want
OL,19,Fto leave the revered Abbey Road
OL,20,Fstudios in London.
