OL,3,CThe return of The Zutons: Liverpool
OL,4,Cband back on the road
OL,6,F"If that hadn't happened I'd probably
OL,7,Fstill be dipping in and out of it," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FAbi Harding agrees adding "We probably
OL,11,Fwouldn't have been here doing this".
OL,13,FBoth say time has flown and somehow
OL,14,Fgone slowly in parts in the last two
OL,15,Fdecades.
OL,17,FAsked if the chemistry in the band is
OL,18,Fthe same Abi said: "It's better, I
OL,19,Fthink it's better than it was before."
